reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased this set to take on a cruise. Please note that the smallest of the four bags is extremely small. Maybe one that she wants to use as a carry-on, and bring your electronics or if you have numerous medical devices and equipment that may work well for you cosmetic, travel, bag, etc.. The other three bags are a very useful size. The other three size bags are very useful for numerous different items whether it be sundries, clothing, shoes, etc. I did buy packing cubes which I highly recommend. I had an amazing experience with them super organized. I was able to take them out unzip them flip the top underneath, and keep my items in my own packing cubes without having to stick them in the drawers, not knowing what might be there. I felt much safer and cleaner. Especially for undergarments and socks. Items that are small, like swimsuits it kept things very organized in my suitcase the suitcases come with amazing Storage and clips that are very similar to the Samsonite bags we already own. The exterior quality was very well-made, and they do come with a combination lock device, which I clipped the pieces in from the zipper. Just ensure the zippers work in a pop open. The handles are amazing super easy to lift these bags. The wheels and telescoping are very high-quality I found These bags to be of a much higher standard than I expected. Although they are lightweight, and they all nest together nicely they are sturdier than I would have expected. The price point is excellent for the quality. I loved having a different color bag that was very easy to detect amongst the sea of standardize colors people choose . I can say I also received a number of compliments. The only downside I could say is that the bags do not stack together so if you’re looking to stack them so you can carry that extra bag you may need or if you have small people that cannot carry their own bags, you may want to purchase us a strap to hold it in place. I chose to tip Porter very well so he brought our bags directly to our car! Lol I now live in the smarter, not harder world where certain things are worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, Spacious, and Stylish - A Fantastic Luggage Set!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Luggage Sets Expandable PC+ABS Durable Suitcase with Double Wheels and TSA Lock in the stunning Blue color, and I must say, I am thoroughly impressed! This luggage set has exceeded my expectations in several ways.First and foremost, durability is paramount when it comes to luggage, and this set delivers on that front. The PC+ABS construction feels rock-solid and capable of withstanding the rigors of travel. Even after a few flights, my luggage still looks brand new with minimal scuffs or scratches.The double wheels are a game-changer. They glide effortlessly, making it a breeze to maneuver through crowded airports or busy streets. Plus, they’re exceptionally quiet, which is a nice touch.The built-in TSA lock provides that extra layer of security, giving me peace of mind during my journeys. It’s simple to set and easy to use, adding to the convenience of this luggage set.Now, let’s talk about space. This set is incredibly spacious! The expandable feature comes in handy when I need a bit of extra room for souvenirs or shopping finds. It’s impressive how much I can fit in these suitcases while still keeping everything organized.The beautiful Blue color is not only aesthetically pleasing but also makes it easy to spot my luggage on the carousel. It stands out in a sea of black and gray suitcases, which is a huge plus.In conclusion, I couldn’t be happier with my purchase of this Luggage Sets Expandable PC+ABS Durable Suitcase with Double Wheels and TSA Lock in Blue. It’s heavy-duty, spacious, stylish, and overall an excellent investment for any traveler. I highly recommend it to anyone in need of reliable luggage that will last for many adventures to come!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight but durable
reviews.reviewText: I bought these about 7 months ago and have been waiting to write a review so I could comment on wear and tear. I travel at least once a month and after 6 months have had no issues with these suitcases. They are so light, but they have held up great with all my travel. Easy to carry and use - the handles go up and down without issues; they roll easily (don’t leave them unattended on a slanted driveway because they will roll away); and they keep my stuff neatly and safely packed inside. All for a reasonable price. I’ll gladly buy these again when they need to be replaced.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The luggage's durability truly stood out, especially given the strenuous conditions of a lengthy flight. I was half-expecting some wear and tear, but it surpassed my expectations by emerging largely unscathed. It's evident that it's designed to handle pressure and wear with resilience.Additionally, its design allows for efficient nesting storage, a feature that several other users have pointed out and appreciated. This is not just a space-saving feature but also indicative of thoughtful design.The color of the luggage is yet another noteworthy aspect. Its unique hue not only adds an aesthetic touch but also serves a functional purpose. It allows for easy identification amidst a sea of common luggage colors, reducing the time spent at baggage claim.While there are some minor imperfections in the form of scratch marks, they're subtle enough to go mostly unnoticed unless one is specifically looking for them. In the grand scheme of things, such minor blemishes are easily overshadowed by the luggage's overall quality and utility.Lastly, the built-in lock mechanism deserves special mention. The convenience of not having to fumble around with separate keys or travel padlocks cannot be understated. It's a feature that adds to the luggage's security without compromising on ease of use.In summary, this luggage is not only functional but also thoughtfully designed, with several features that enhance the travel experience. Hopefully, it lasts longer than expected from hard case luggage.

I got the set to replace my old luggage. It has the perfect sizes for a long trip of a family of 4.Quality: I already used them for a couple of trips (4 flights) and stand perfectly the hard manipulation at the airports. I used big one and middle one at the top 23kg each...and the carry on at the top of 10kg. All come with perfect pockets and zipper inside to split it in half. The most impressive were the wheels! are very good quality and run very smoothly and strong at the same time. The 4 sizes can cover almost every need and the 2 small ones are perfect as carry on luggage. Handlers provide a perfect grip and telescopic handlers goes up and down easily.Last but not least, the color is PERFECT to identify them at the bad at first sight.After the 4 flights, it was expected some scratches and dirty, so I cleaned them up before to store them in the garage. Another big hit is to keep them all stores as only ONE...all the 3 small ones fit into each other so is very convenient to store.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excelente producto por relación calidad/Precio recomendada
reviews.reviewText: Espere un poco para poder usarlas y dar mi opinión con uso. La maleta chica la he usado constantemente, mi trabajo me requiere estar practicamente 3 semanas fuera del mes, la uso en mi carro y como maleta de cabina en vuelos, primero que nada me resisitia a este tipo de maletas, tenía 3 años usando una Samsonite de tela, la maleta es sorprendente en su capacidad, mi maleta vieja esa mas grande (24") y es comparable, hasta el momento ha resistido bien y con gran capacidad. La maleta grande hice un viaje de León- México- Amsterdam- Tel-Aviv. salí con 25 kgs y regresé con 29kgs sin problema alguna, rodó muy bien en los aeropuertos con el peso y todo se ve bien. Los rayones son de esperarse, aunque en realidad no la veo muy dañada. Espero cuando menos 2 años de uso en la pequeña y con las otras no las uso tanto, mi esposa compró una Samsonite Mediana, será punto de comparación. Contento con la compra.

reviews.reviewTitle: LE VALIGIE CHE HO SEMPRE DESIDERATO
reviews.reviewText: Finalmente, dopo tanti acquisti inutili, ho trovato le valigie dei miei desideri: un set davvero completo, con 4 valigie belle a vedersi, dai colori originali e brillanti, ben fatte nei materiali, tessuti e cuciture, dotate ognuna di comodi scomparti a cerniera, chiusure di sicurezza con combinazione e possibilità di apertura alla dogana con la chiave apposita, ruote doppie girevoli alla grande. Le valigie sono utilizzabili per tutte le necessità grazie alle 4 diverse dimensioni, inseribili perfettamente una nell'altra per la massima compattezza quando devono essere riposte al ritorno dal viaggio.Per il rapporto qualità prezzo posso confermare che si tratta di un ottimo acquisto, il migliore che abbia mai fatto in tema di valigie, la soluzione definitiva!
Fué para un regalo y por ahora están muy contentos.El color es precioso.
